org.gcn.plinguacore.simulator

Class ElementFileStream<ElementType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gcn.plinguacore.simulator.ElementFileStream<ElementType>
  • Type Parameters:
    ElementType - The element type to be saved and loaded
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ElementFileStream<ElementType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class gives support for storing and loading different elements, according to ElementType class. The elements this class is intended for are Simulators and P-systems
    Author:
    Research Group on Natural Computing (http://www.gcn.us.es)
    See Also:
